Package: mapmate
Title: Make Still Image Sequences For Data Animations
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Matthew Leonawicz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matthew Leonawicz <mfleonawicz@alaska.edu>
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Leonawicz", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mfleonawicz@alaska.edu")
Description: mapmate is an R package for generating and saving a sequence of
    map- and globe-based plots to disk as a still image sequence intended for later use in data animation
    production.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    mapproj,
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    ggplot2,
    RcppRoll,
    shiny,
    lazyeval,
    geosphere
